{"tid":398484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被外媒說買不起iPhone8　中國網民嗆：我們有華為","createTime":"2017-09-13T08:45:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T13:25:37.000Z","uid":75969,"like":108,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f89ba9978f08972abdbc2cf8a9d9a5b9bf302c5c","tid":398484,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T08:45:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170913/640_3f0a9b6c316d4cc6a7a7f2ab82bceb11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170913%2F640_3f0a9b6c316d4cc6a7a7f2ab82bceb11.jpg&h=a16831cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">蘋果最新一代智慧型手機「iPhone 8」發表在即，卻被外媒《路透社》唱衰，直言「1000美元的售價太貴了，中國人買不起」。示意照。翻攝網路</span><br />\n<br />\n蘋果最新一代智慧型手機「iPhone 8」發表在即，卻被外媒《路透社》唱衰，直言「1000美元的售價太貴了，中國人買不起」，恐怕無助提振iPhone在亞洲市場日益疲軟的市佔率，沒想到消息傳回中國國內，意外引發中國網民群情激憤、一陣撻伐，「為什麼不買？因為我們有華為了啊！」<br />\n<br />\n根據《路透社》的報導指出，對於蘋果來說，這一代iPhone能否在中國成功是至關重要的，尤其在經歷了一段低潮期之後，曾經被大家「覬覦」的iPhone地位已經不復存在，目前蘋果手機在中國市場僅僅排名第5，還落後於中國的國產品牌華為、Oppo、Vivo和小米。<br />\n<br />\n儘管新一代iPhone新增了無線充電、先進觸碰螢幕和臉部識別技術，但還是沒能複制之前iPhone推出時中國網絡上熱議的盛大景象，《路透社》認為，關鍵就在定價，「面對價格將高達1000美元甚至更貴的iPhone 8，約等同於中國人均月工資的2倍，中國消費者很可能會望之卻步。」<br />\n<br />\n結果這篇報導被中國媒體以「路透社唱衰iPhone8：太貴了　中國人買不起」為題大肆報導，許多中國網民看到新聞都十分氣憤，「激將法，不上當」、<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「不是我們買不起蘋果，而是蘋果已經配不上我」、「信不信我們中國人給路透社買下來！」</strong></span>（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170913/1202661/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170913%2F1202661%2F&d=LKBbiYzuyBUmF83r8VakxghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=6cfde0cd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170913/1202661/</a><br />\n<br />\nmolamola 連強國人都唔買 apple已死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59e1bc89006414d866c33ade4b7cbb63ccd396b1","tid":398484,"uid":17089,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T08:46:51.000Z","msg":"哎喲 成地玻璃囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2eb0a54513a7db7c39e223b8a9d321ac03b91a5","tid":398484,"uid":8716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T08:46:57.000Z","msg":"最好唔好買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae73337221cece2053cb50d7ffa7c4f8ddae5bd9","tid":398484,"uid":143241,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T08:49:05.000Z","msg":"買咗死全族"},{"pid":"378011e2e5e336b0567ac4f874f93120a8bcb6d8","tid":398484,"uid":9286,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T08:49:11.000Z","msg":"iPhone 8，約等同於中國人均月工資的2倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9347c53bb2f4275613e9ce016de5e76777f61b60","tid":398484,"uid":57835,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T08:57:26.000Z","msg":"華為算中國牌子中最好嗰個"},{"pid":"8491525cd81677153ff9c0a8f5bbaf94b53cbabb","tid":398484,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T09:18:19.000Z","msg":"咪姐係買唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a7fabb4c8fb96a608531baea5abf0753fef34db","tid":398484,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T09:20:34.000Z","msg":"唔洗激將法啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a4b9534b13f6d9719c8cdf8fe4342a962df1c5","tid":398484,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T09:31:54.000Z","msg":"買唔起買得起同你地有華為有乜關係"},{"pid":"8a421dd0c10bea6b2b6ea4d4a5025fbee2fdf7ab","tid":398484,"uid":49588,"like":8,"dis